Before run 
firstly, you should make sure you have some basic tools in your linux.
check if qemu,(bochs) are in your computer.
if not, install them.
in ubuntu, run
$apt install -y qemu bochs bochs-x bximage

Run method
just execute run.sh in linux enviroment
in ubuntu, try
$sudo  ./run.sh
